{"tid":390443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（齊鼓掌）親共副局長之子墜樓亡！","createTime":"2017-09-07T06:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T10:44:35.000Z","uid":29314,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f63d8bbbc817f86024d40a7d0b8e7b0188a8abd","tid":390443,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:04:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170907/mobile/bkn-20170907121455773-0907_00822_001.html \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170907%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170907121455773-0907_00822_001.html%20&d=9KuE1y%2Fp8HLmKs9zaf6rKpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=6c56b770\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170907/mobile/bkn-20170907121455773-0907_00822_001.html </a><br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀柯士甸道擎天半島發生墮樓案，早上11時許，大廈保安員突聞巨響，發現一名20餘歲男子倒臥在第3座平台對開，一臉鮮血陷入昏迷，於是報警。救護員及消防員到場，為傷者急救後送院，惜告死亡。警方初步相信男子由40多層高墮下，正調查其墮樓原因。&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74dc055bb4b4bc33a9d62c4ea4659289a112d9fb","tid":390443,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:16:03.000Z","msg":"Is that Karma?"},{"pid":"c17f34e43732acea0209f2cdb75077c7fef1285c","tid":390443,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:44:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Is that Karma?</blockquote><br />\n爹親娘親不及毛主席親！"}]}